videos.description: Remy Martin smacks a wide-open dunk to give Arizona State a 2-point lead over Arizona.
videos.headline: Martin crushes two-handed slam

videos.description: With 5 seconds left on the shot clock, Remy Martin throws the ball up and sinks a deep 3-pointer.
videos.headline: Martin tosses up deep 3 as shot clock winds down

videos.description: Ryan Luther delivers a 3-pointer to close Arizona State's lead to 55-52.
videos.headline: Luther's 3 pulls Arizona within 3

videos.description: Zylan Cheatham crushes a dunk in transition to keep Arizona State in the lead in a tight game.
videos.headline: Cheatham hits alley-oop dunk

videos.description: With 25 seconds left in regulation, Arizona's Justin Coleman knocks down a 3-pointer to tie the game at 83-83.
videos.headline: Coleman ties game late with 3

videos.description: Arizona state head coach Bobby Hurley gets hit in the face with a ball hit out of bounds, and  falls to the floor.
videos.headline: ASU's Bobby Hurley hit in face with ball
